ref=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/IsManifold/Basic.html#modelWithCornersSelf\">modelWithCornersSelf</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> <span class=\"fn\">F_fiber</span>)</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span>\n            <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">M</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Bundle.html#Bundle.TotalSpace.mk'\">Bundle.TotalSpace.mk'</a> <span class=\"fn\">F_fiber</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s_loc</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span>)</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">U_x₀</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a>           <span class=\"fn\">∀ <span class=\"fn\">y</span> ∈ <span class=\"fn\">U_x₀</span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s_loc</span> <span class=\"fn\">y</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">t</span> <span class=\"fn\">y</span></span></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/VectorBundle/SmoothSection.html#ContMDiffSection\">ContMDiffSection</a> <span class=\"fn\">I</span> <span class=\"fn\">F_fiber</span> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">V</span></span>), <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">M</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">t</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"**Alias** of `exists_contMDiffSection_forall_mem_convex_of_local`.\n\n---\n\nLet `V` be a vector bundle over a σ-compact Hausdorff finite-dimensional topological manifold\n`M`. Let `t : M → Set (V x)` be a family of convex sets in the fibers of `V`.\nSuppose that for each point `x₀ : M` there exists a neighborhood `U_x₀` of `x₀` and a local\nsection `s_loc : M → V x` such that `s_loc` is $C^n$ smooth on `U_x₀` (when viewed as a map to\nthe total space of the bundle) and `s_loc y ∈ t y` for all `y ∈ U_x₀`.\nThen there exists a global $C^n$ smooth section `s : Cₛ^n⟮I_M; F_fiber, V⟯` such that\n`s x ∈ t x` for all `x : M`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/PartitionOfUnity.html#exists_smooth_section_forall_mem_convex_of_local","kind":"theorem","line":652,"name":"exists_smooth_section_forall_mem_convex_of_local","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/PartitionOfUnity.lean#L652-L654"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/PartitionOfUnity.html#exists_contMDiffOn_section_forall_mem_convex_of_local\"><span class=\"name\">exists_contMDiffOn_section_forall_mem_convex_of_local</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> uE}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#NormedAddCommGroup\">NormedAddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Basic.html#NormedSpace\">NormedSpace</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">H</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\"